name: MyWeddSpace
overview:
MyWeddSpace.pl is a state-of-the-art and technology-driven wedding portal designed to satisfy all the needs of couples, from the moment of their engagement until their wedding day; namely through trendy and updated content, useful tools and the broadest catalogue of wedding suppliers. One of their most innovative features is the launch of the first online wedding gift list in Poland, with discounts for couples in top international brands. Similar website concepts are present in some other countries â€“ US, UK, Spain, France… â€“ although in Poland it has no comparable at the moment.

MyWeddS.pl was launched back in June 2010 by a group of private investors led by Spanish entrepreneur Alvaro Figar.
